Board SDK

You can access the SDK through the Board Developer Portal. The SDK includes a Simulator and Board Developer Bridge (BDB). You can grab builds for macOS, Linux, and Windows. This utility allows you to install, launch, and log applications running the Board SDK. 
 
You can also review the full documentation and Developer FAQs here.
 
